Following are the assumptions on the pet feeder machine.
i.	The feeder machine will dispense food on time ( for e.g. 8 AM and 6 PM).
ii.	The feeder machine will be connected to real time clock in order to follow the feeding time mechanism.
iii.	The feeder machine is able to access internet to send alerts to the shelter staff.
iv.	The shelter staff will regularly refill the food bin.
v.	The food tray is pet friendly. 
